events.name: We're hijacking Kopi.JS!
events.description:
Hey DevFest.Asia 2016 Organisers! 

Thanks so much for being a part of our second running of DevFest.Asia! Thomas and I would like to invite you to this month's Kopi.JS and chat about any exciting updates/questions/uncertainties left! 

DevFest.Asia is fast approaching and it'll be great for all the Community Organisers to meet each other and hang out :) 

We're super excited to get this running with you, so PLEASE PUT THIS IN YOUR CALENDAR and we'll see you for some awesome Kopi/ Kaya Toast!

*There will be stickers :D
events.location: Ya Kun Kaya Toast, China Street, 18 China Street #01-01, Singapore 049560
